In [17]:
train_dataset=dataset.sample(frac=.8,random_state=0)

In [18]:

In [260]:
model=Sequential()
model.add(normalizer)
for i in range(7):
    model.add(Dense(8,activation='relu'))
model.add(Dense(3,activation='softmax'))
